OL,6,FA school and welfare officer and
OL,7,Fformer Army Cadet leader was remanded
OL,8,Finto custody today after he was
OL,9,Fconvicted by a jury of sexually
OL,10,Fabusing teenage girls.
OL,12,FAs a result of the guilty verdicts
OL,13,FNeil Clarke Beckett - who is currently
OL,14,Fsuspended from his role at Lagan
OL,15,FCollege in south Belfast - was told by
OL,16,FJudge Philip Gilpin "you are, from
OL,17,Fthis point on, a registered sex
OL,18,Foffender".
