OL,6,FThe Judge also told Beckett that the
OL,7,Flength of time he will spend on the
OL,8,FSex Offenders' Register will be
OL,9,Fdetermined when he is sentenced in
OL,10,FDecember on a total of 17 charges.
OL,12,FThe 43-year-old father of one, from
OL,13,FKilmore Village in Downpatrick, stood
OL,14,Ftrial on a total of 29 charges against
OL,15,Fnine teenagers which he denied.
OL,17,FThese charges consisted of one count
OL,18,Fof rape, one count of sexual
OL,19,Fcommunication with a child, one count
OL,20,Fof sexual grooming and 26 counts of
OL,21,Fsexual assault.
