OL,6,FAfter deliberating for over two days,
OL,7,Fthe jury of six men and six women
OL,8,Freturned 'unanimous' verdicts on all
OL,9,Fthe charges today at Belfast Crown
OL,10,FCourt.
OL,12,FBeckett was acquitted of the rape
OL,13,Fcharge, of sexual communication with a
OL,14,Fchild and ten counts of sexual abuse.
OL,16,FHe was found guilty of 17 charges he
OL,17,Ffaced - namely one count of sexual
OL,18,Fgrooming and 16 counts of sexual
OL,19,Fassault.
