OL,6,FThese offences were committed between
OL,7,F2015 and 2023.
OL,9,FWhilst he was cleared of raping and
OL,10,Fsexually assaulting an Army cadet, he
OL,11,Fwas convicted of sexually grooming her.
OL,13,FHe was also convicted of sexually
OL,14,Fabusing a second Army cadet by
OL,15,Fhugging, kissing and tickling her.
OL,17,FRegarding the Lagan College pupils,
OL,18,FBeckett was convicted of sexually
OL,19,Fabusing seven pupils and acquitted of
OL,20,Foffences against a further two
OL,21,Fcomplainants.
