OL,10,FCrown barrister David McNeill said
OL,11,FBeckett had been convicted of sexual
OL,12,Foffences against nine victims over the
OL,13,Fcourse of up to eight years.
OL,15,FThe Judge said that due to guilty
OL,16,Fconvictions against nine children,
OL,17,Fthere was "a certain inevitability in
OL,18,Fwhat may occur".
